19920728000000000_9	In a traditional plant sheet is made by pouring liquid steel into a mould shaping it into red hot slabs between 8 and 12 inches thick and 30 to 40 feet long.	tradit plant sheet made pour liquid steel mould shape red hot slab inch thick feet long
